<FIRST>u f BC-TheWeekAhead     08-04 0263</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-The Week Ahead,0293</SECOND>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
 Here are the major business events and economic events scheduled for the coming week -LRB- some dates are tentative; times are EDT -RRB-:
</TEXT>
